{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "第一回「七个瞎子」讲述了风四娘在乱石山洗澡时，被七个神秘瞎子闯入。瞎子们手持明杖和扇子，扇子上写着「必杀萧十一郎」，他们要挟风四娘跟随他们走。风四娘试图反抗，但瞎子们展示出高超的武功和冷酷的决心。此时，一个跛子出现带领瞎子们，风四娘发现跛子剑法熟悉。随后，枫林中出现心心姑娘，她为风四娘送来衣服，自称是花公子花如玉的侍女。心心与跛子交手，展现出惊人武功。关键时刻，一个四肢残缺、坐在巨人头上的鞭客出现，用长鞭制服心心。鞭客冷酷无情，逼迫心心自断毒手，并透露自己曾因中毒自残。风四娘试图为心心求情，但鞭客坚持「人上人」哲学。整个章节充满紧张对峙和神秘氛围，引出萧十一郎的仇恨线索。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连瞎子都要来看我洗澡，我的魔力倒真不小。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你没有穿衣服？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们洗澡的时候穿衣服？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我们等你穿起衣服来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们既然看不见我，那我又何必穿衣服？我真替你们可惜，像我这么好看的女人在洗澡，你们居然看不见，实在是件很遗憾的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不遗憾。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不遗憾？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞎子也是人，虽然不能看，却可以摸，不但可以摸，还可以做很多别的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你最好老实些，我们叫你穿衣服，你最好就赶快穿衣服。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是想要我干什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要你跟着我们走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有眼睛的人，反而要跟着没有眼睛的人走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论你们到哪里，我都跟你们到哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们若是掉进粪坑里去，我也得跟着跳下去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说的并不是笑话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我却觉得很好笑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好笑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们凭什么认为我会听你们的话？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不凭什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们虽然瞎，却并不聋，难道从来也没有听说过，风四娘洗澡的时候，身上也一样带着杀人的利器，也一样能杀人的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们听说过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你们一点也不怕？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对我们说来，天下已经没有可怕的事了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死你们都不怕？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们已不必怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我们都已死过一次。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "偷看我洗澡的人，眼睛都一定会瞎的，只可惜你们本来就已经是瞎子了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "实在可惜。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好我虽然没法子让你们再瞎一次，却可以要你们再死一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可怜的萧十一郎，为什么总是有这么多人要你死呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他该死！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都跟他有仇？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你们的眼睛，就是因为他才会瞎的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说过，我们都已死过一次。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我们现在都已不是以前那个人，那个人已死在萧十一郎手里！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们以前是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以前我们至少是个有名有姓的人，现在却已只不过是个瞎子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你们也想要他死一次？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非死不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然如此，你们就应该找他去，为什么来找我？我又不是他的娘。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是来干什么的？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里是乱石山，乱石山是强盗窝，我恰巧有个老朋友也是强盗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快刀花平？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们也知道他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "关中群盗的总瓢把子，江湖中有谁不知道？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们既然知道他，就应该让我去找他。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不必？不必是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这意思就是说，你若要见他，我随时都可以叫他来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他难道也很听你们的话？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他知道瞎子也杀人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "送花平进来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来好像这只不过是个盒子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花平好像并不是个盒子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为何不打开盒子来看看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花平难道还会藏在这盒子里？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来我只怕已永远见不到这个人了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你总该明白，你若要一个人去死，并不一定要砍下他脑袋来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我们只要毁了你这张脸，你也就等于死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我最好还是乖乖的穿起衣服，跟你们走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "瞎子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们这些瞎了眼的王八蛋，你们真看错人了，你们也不打听打听，风四娘活了三十……岁，几时听过别人话的？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们若想请我到什么地方去，至少也该先拍拍我的马屁，再找顶轿子来抬我，那么我也许还可以考虑考虑。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到我居然会在这里遇见一个君子，居然好像从来也没有看见过女人洗澡的君子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，前面那位一条腿先生，你既是个君子，就该把身上的衣服脱下来给我穿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "停车爱看枫林晚，霜叶红于二月花……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "风四娘果然是风四娘，这种时候，她居然还有心情吟诗。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好漂亮的小姑娘……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜这个小姑娘在风四娘面前一比，就变成个小丑八怪了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像这样一个又聪明、又漂亮的小姑娘，总不会是跟这些怪物一路的吧？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫心心，是特地来送衣服给风四娘的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心心，好美的名字，简直就跟人一样美。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们虽然不知四娘衣裳的尺寸，可是这么好身材的人，无论穿什么衣裳，都一定会好看的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像这么样好心的小姑娘，将来一定能找得到如意郎君的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好心的不是我，是我们家的花公子。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花公子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他知道四娘来得匆忙，没有穿衣裳，山上的风又大，怕四娘着了凉，所以特地要我送这套衣裳来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来这位花公子，倒是一个很体贴的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他本来就是的，不但体贴，而且温柔极了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我却好像并不认得这样一位花公子呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在虽然还不认得，但以后就会认得的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，又有谁是一生出来就认得的呢？能认得这样一个温柔体贴的男人，无论什么样的女人都不会反对的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花公子本来也只希望四娘能记得世上还有他这样一个男人。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我绝对忘不了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你凭什么要人家站住？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的花公子，是不是花如玉？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了花如玉花公子外，世上还有哪位花公子会这么温柔体贴？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你问他干什么？难道你想去找他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也知道你不敢去找他的，所以我告诉你也没有用。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "跛子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这衣服你带回去，花如玉碰过的东西就有毒，我们不要。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们不要，我要！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然四娘要，你们还不赶快把衣服送过去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怕什么？这些人的样子虽然凶，但却绝不敢拦住你们的……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是你先出手的，你自己要找倒楣，可怨不得我。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是不是说过你要倒楣的，你现在总该相信了吧？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你跪在地上，乖乖的叫我三声姑奶奶，我就饶了你。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我问你，你究竟肯不肯叫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真忍心杀我？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是他先动手的，你不信可以问他自己。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只不过是奉花公子之命，来送衣裳给风四娘的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然你全都知道，我是不是可以走了？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你当然可以走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的鞭子上有毒？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是有一点。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那……那怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道我这两条腿，一只手，是怎么断的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我自己砍断的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么要砍断自己的手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我手上中了别人的毒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你难道也想要我变成个残废？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "残废又如何？这里的人岂非全都是残废？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他就不是残废。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真要我自己把这只手砍下来？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "手上有毒，就要砍手，腿上有毒，就要砍腿。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_xin",
      "speaker_name": "心心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是……可是我舍不得。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若也舍不得，现在已死过三次。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她怎么能跟你比，她是个女人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人也是人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也是人，你凭什么要坐在别人的头上？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我本就是人上人。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人上人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吃得苦中苦，就是人上人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你吃过苦中苦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "这人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若也割下自己两条腿，一只手来，你就知道我是不是吃过苦中苦了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 682
    }
  ],
